   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>To my lord brother Isidoros, Claudianus. Please give Chrestos the thirty solidi which I furnished on your behalf to my lord Euxitheus, and the other five expended on account of the grain, and the other three on account of the mare, and the other one on account of the camel. If you do not do this, know that I can put an end to all the benefactions which I effected for you. Please furnish to the said Chrestos the other fourteen measures of grass-seed.;(2nd hand) I pray for your continued good health.</ab>
